NBA, Players Union Representatives Will Continue Contract Talks Tomorrow

-- B y   R o b   G l o s t e r
-- 
2011-10-03T20:06:15Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-10-03/nba-players-union-representatives-will-continue-contract-talks-tomorrow.html
Talks between National Basketball
Association officials and representatives of the players union
have ended for the day after a five-hour meeting at a New York
hotel, and the sides plan to meet again tomorrow.  NBA Deputy Commissioner Adam Silver said today’s meeting
“set the table” for tomorrow’s negotiating session as the
sides try to reach an agreement that will allow the NBA season
to begin on time on Nov. 1.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Rob Gloster at 
 rgloster@bloomberg.net  